These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, davidoff, montecristo, cain
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, r&b, salsa, techno
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, colombian, indonesian, polish
There are 4 different favourite colors: amber, black, ebony, aquamarine
1. the colombian is the fan of techno##1
2. the indonesian is between the montecristo-smoker and the cain-smoker##2
3. the colombian is the person who likes amber##1
4. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person who likes amber##1
5. the fan of metal is on the left of the canadian##1
6. the person who likes ebony is the montecristo-smoker##1
7. the fan of r&b is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
8. the canadian is on the far right##1
9. the davidoff-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Cigar   | davidoff | cain   | game  | montecristo  |
| Music-Genre   | r&b    | techno    | metal      | salsa    |
| Nationality   | polish | colombian | indonesian | canadian |
| Color     | aquamarine  | amber       | black    | ebony     |

