.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, singing, woodworking
There are 4 different favourite colors: fuchsia, turquise, grey, blood-red
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, manager, paramedic, photographer
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, lacrosse, swimming, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far right##1
3. the photographer is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
5. the person who likes blood-red is between the paramedic and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
6. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the person who likes blood-red and the photographer##2
7. the electrician is on the far right##1
8. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
9. the person who likes grey is on the right of the manager##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | woodworking | drawing    | singing  | cooking    |
| Color   | fuchsia      | turquise  | blood-red  | grey |
| Job           | photographer      | paramedic       | manager      | electrician       |
| Sport         | lacrosse    | water-polo | swimming | ice-hockey |

