.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
There are 4 different nationalities: british, french, turkish, german
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, december, february, august
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, lawyer, paramedic, pilot
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike, roller, subway
1. the paramedic is the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the pilot##1
3. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the turkish is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
6. the lawyer is the person who's birthday is in august##1
7. the german is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
8. the british is between the person who's birthday is in september and the person who's birthday is in august##2
9. the person who's birthday is in february is between the turkish and the lawyer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Nationality        | french | turkish     | british   | german     |
| Birthday       | december   | september   | february | august |
| Job         | analyst   | paramedic | pilot       | lawyer    |
| Transport   | roller    | motorbike | helicopter  | subway    |

