.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, tea, lemonade
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, boat, subway, jet-ski
4 different pets are kept: bird, frog, hamster, pony
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, rugby, soccer, volleyball
 1. the person driving the boat is on the far right##1
 2. the person driving the jet-ski is the person drinking coffee##1
 3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the jet-ski is the owner of the frog##1
 6. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 7. the person driving the boat is the person drinking tea##1
 8. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 9. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
10. the person drinking cola is between the owner of the bird and the person drinking lemonade##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Beverage           | coffee  | lemonade | cola     | tea |
| Transport   | jet-ski | bus  | subway | boat       |
| Pet           | frog       | pony    | hamster      | bird           |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | rugby   | volleyball   | soccer         |

