.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-5::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, garlic, lemon, peach
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, lemonade, sprite, tea
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, epic, romance, scientific
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, aconite, poppy, iris
 1. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
 2. the person who growszinnia is on the far left##1
 3. the person drinking sprite is the person eating garlic##1
 4. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person eating peach##1
 6. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
 7. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
 8. the person drinking lemonade is the person watching epic movies##1
 9. the person eating lemon is between the person who growsiris and the person watching adventure movies##2
10. the person watching romance movies is the person who growspoppy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Food          | garlic         | lemon         | asparagus     | peach      |
| Beverage           | sprite | tea | fanta    | lemonade     |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure      | romance       | scientific    | epic       |
| Flower         | zinnia     | poppy       | iris | aconite |

