The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, funk, jazz, punk
City: hamburg, liverpool, hannover, berlin
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cricket, cycling, sailing
1. the fan of folk is between the person who's sport is sailing and the fan of jazz##2
2. the person eating nectarine is between the fan of folk and the person traveling to berlin##2
3. the person traveling to hannover is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person traveling to liverpool##2
4. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
5. the person traveling to hannover is the person traveling to hannover##1
6. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
7. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1
8. the fan of jazz is on the far right##1
9. the fan of funk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Food           | eggplant | nectarine | blueberry  | pear |
| Music-Genre   | funk      | punk       | folk     | jazz      |
| City   | berlin   | liverpool      | hannover   | hamburg   |
| Sport         | cycling   | sailing    | climbing | cricket   |

